な作業でしたが…\r\n自分の家が出来上がる感覚がとても楽しくて、思い出深い作業となりました！\r\n色選びも3ヶ月は悩んだかも。\r\nペンキを塗ったことで唯一無二の自分の部屋になりました！ありがとうございます！'),(2599,414,'spec04','築28年'),(2600,416,'_wp_attached_file','2017/08/IMG_0395.jpg'),(2601,416,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:3088;s:6:\"height\";i:2056;s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"2017/08/IMG_0395.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:12:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"IMG_0395-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"IMG_0395-300x200.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:200;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:12:\"medium_large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"IMG_0395-768x511.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:768;s:6:\"height\";i:511;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:5:\"large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"IMG_0395-1024x682.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:1024;s:6:\"height\";i:682;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:5:\"event\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"IMG_0395-380x210.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:380;s:6:\"height\";i:210;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:4:\"work\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"IMG_0395-880x460.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:880;s:6:\"height\";i:460;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:5:\"thumb\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:19:\"IMG_0395-101x80.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:101;s:6:\"height\";i:80;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"detail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"IMG_0395-400x260.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:400;s:6:\"height\";i:260;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"madori\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"IMG_0395-433x288.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:433;s:6:\"height\";i:288;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:5:\"voice\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"IMG_0395-150x160.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:160;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:4:\"list\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:20:\"IMG_0395-310x200.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:310;s:6:\"height\";i:200;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:14:\"post-thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"IMG_0395-1200x799.jpg\";s:5:\"width\"